libbtctl: libbtctl (Gobject Library Bluetooth Controller)
libbtctl:
libbtctl: This library is intended to provide a GLib style library of 
libbtctl: application support for accessing common platform Bluetooth functions 
libbtctl: under Linux, and is used by GNOME Bluetooth applications and GNOME
libbtctl: Phone Manager require. It can also be used as a stand alone library
libbtctl: as it does not require GNOME libraries.
libbtctl: 
libbtctl: For more information, please see http://live.gnome.org/GnomeBluetooth
